# Tabular mode with packed sub-struct cells
# Format: @tab Type [columns]\n row1\n row2\n ... @end
# Nested structs in cells use packed format

# -----------------------------------------------------
# Match table: 3+ rows triggers tabular mode
# Columns are ordered by FID, wire keys used
# -----------------------------------------------------
@tab Match [m k H A O P fh fa]
^m:ARS-LIV 2025-12-19T20:00:00Z Team@(^t:ARS Arsenal EPL) Team@(^t:LIV Liverpool EPL) Odds@(2.1 3.4 3.25) Pred@(0.45 0.27 0.28 1.72 1.31) 2 1
^m:MCI-CHE 2025-12-20T15:00:00Z Team@(^t:MCI "Manchester City" EPL) Team@(^t:CHE Chelsea EPL) Odds@(1.8 3.6 4.2) Pred@(0.52 0.24 0.24 1.85 1.15) ∅ ∅
^m:TOT-MUN 2025-12-21T17:30:00Z Team@(^t:TOT Tottenham EPL) Team@(^t:MUN "Manchester United" EPL) Odds@(2.5 3.3 2.8) Pred@(0.38 0.27 0.35 1.45 1.55) 1 1
@end

