# -----------------------------------------------------
# Inline tabular (for nested list<struct> in packed parent)
# Uses | separator for rows within a single line
# -----------------------------------------------------
@tab Team [t n l] ^t:ARS Arsenal EPL | ^t:LIV Liverpool EPL | ^t:CHE Chelsea EPL @end
